{
  "stem": "23832.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started-- they made a military, paramilitary unit in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave them a cap like the policeman, except this one was here, royal blue, like they put on a [NON-ENGLISH] You know what that is?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were the arm of the Germans to destroy us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In meantime, when you are a doctor, or a nurse, or a midwife, you got from-- from the medical [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] establishment a certificate.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not a-- it's a little bit folded like this-- that you are a nurse, or you are a doctor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the beginning, you were immune from being taken-- in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, though this time, my doctor paid money to the Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's all fake.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Polish people, the Polish group-- I don't know-- they were in good standing with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans let them make toy, wooden toy factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my husband paid them a lot of money to have a paper that he's employed in that place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the Germans didn't allow us to have furs of no kind, even those that you have to have pieces, or a whole.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My husband had a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they used to come to the ghetto and pay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They could come in and out to take anything and everything they could have a hand in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they came to-- to get that sofa, which was-- could be opened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they put my fur coat-- I said, these pieces, I just burned them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just burned those.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the whole coat, brand new, I didn't want them to burn it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I didn't want them to have it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I put it inside the sofa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My husband's friends got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
